Package in.co.rays.bean

Class UserBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.co.rays.bean.BaseBean
      • in.co.rays.bean.UserBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DropdownListBean
    public class UserBean
extends BaseBean
    UserBean represents a system user with personal and login-related details. It extends BaseBean to inherit common fields like id, createdBy, etc.
    Version:
    1.0
